text: BING NEWS: Jiri Vesely Beats Gerald Melzer to Reach 2nd Round in Vienna Jiri Vesely of Czech Republic defeated Austrian wildcard entry Gerald Melzer of Austria 6-4, 6-3 on the opening day of the Erste Bank Open on Monday.
